<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer13701412413099778521">Michelle McNamara was a screenwriter, journalist, and true crime writer. She was the founder of the blog &quot;True Crime Diary,&quot; which covers lesser-known crimes and cold cases. In 2005, she married comedian <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2824524.Patton_Oswalt' title='Patton Oswalt' rel='nofollow noopener'>Patton Oswalt</a>. They had one daughter together, born in 2009.</span>
  <span id="freeText13701412413099778521" style="display:none">Michelle McNamara was a screenwriter, journalist, and true crime writer. She was the founder of the blog "True Crime Diary," which covers lesser-known crimes and cold cases. In 2005, she married comedian <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2824524.Patton_Oswalt" title="Patton Oswalt" rel="nofollow noopener">Patton Oswalt</a>. They had one daughter together, born in 2009.</span>
